--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
INFORMATION
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This file lists changes made to the Ansible role. It follows semantic versioning
guidelines. The content is sorted in reverse chronological order and formatted
to allow easy grepping by scripts.

The fields are:
B: bug
C: change
E: enhancement
F: feature

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

* Version 0.10.0 (2020-07-03)
C: Move scripts to '/usr/local/sbin'
E: Remove 'common' role dependency

* Version 0.9.0 (2020-05-19)
F: Add support for OpenBSD 6.7
F: Drop support for OpenBSD 6.6

* Version 0.8.0 (2019-11-08)
C: Add support for FreeBSD 12.1-RELEASE
C: Drop support for FreeBSD 12.0-RELEASE

* Version 0.7.0 (2019-10-18)
C: Add support for OpenBSD 6.6
C: Drop support for OpenBSD 6.5

* Version 0.6.0 (2019-05-26)
F: Port role to Ansible 2.8

* Version 0.5.0 (2019-04-27)
C: Add support for OpenBSD 6.5
C: Drop support for OpenBSD 6.4

* Version 0.4.3 (2019-01-24)
C: Rename option 'restic_monitor_mail_recipient' to 'restic_monitor_mail_from_address'
C: Rename option 'restic_monitor_mail_sender' to 'restic_monitor_mail_to_address'

* Version 0.4.2 (2019-01-22)
E: Improve script by throwing error message if script is executed interactively

* Version 0.4.1 (2019-01-21)
E: Improve script and reduce noise by removing echo command from alerting function

* Version 0.4.0 (2019-01-14)
C: Add support for FreeBSD 12.0-RELEASE
C: Drop support for FreeBSD 11.2-RELEASE

* Version 0.3.6 (2018-12-19)
E: Minor style improvement

* Version 0.3.5 (2018-12-10)
B: Fix 'mailx' command for OpenBSD systems

* Version 0.3.4 (2018-12-07)
E: Remove 'restic_monitor_mail_subject' parameter

* Version 0.3.3 (2018-12-07)
E: Remove email information from message

* Version 0.3.2 (2018-12-04)
B: Fix 'limit-download' and 'limit-upload' variables in script

* Version 0.3.1 (2018-11-27)
E: Minor style improvements

* Version 0.3.0 (2018-11-19)
C: Add support for 'limit-download' option (restic_limit_download)
C: Add support for 'limit-upload' option (restic_limit_upload)

* Version 0.2.0 (2018-10-20)
C: Add support for OpenBSD 6.4
C: Drop support for OpenBSD 6.3

* Version 0.1.3 (2018-09-14)
E: Add 'no_log' parameter to sensitive tasks

* Version 0.1.2 (2018-08-28)
E: Ensure user's home directory is being removed during remove sequence

* Version 0.1.1 (2018-07-21)
B: Fix remove tags

* Version 0.1.0 (2018-07-21)
F: Initial release
